# QuadAnimationSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Sole writer of QuadComponent's colour and sole adder of AnimationTransformRequestOneFrameComponent.
Each frame, for every entity carrying a SpinComponent and a QuadComponent, advances the spin's
accumulated time (scaled by the DebugControls animation-speed multiplier when present, otherwise 1.0),
recomputes the quad's colour (constant base colour, or an animated cycle when m_ColorCycleSpeed is
non-zero), and emits a transform request carrying the quad's animated position (anchor + optional
orbit) and rotation (about z). Scale and bounds are set once at spawn, not here.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| DebugControlsSingletonComponent | read | Optional animation-speed multiplier; defaults to 1.0 when absent |
| SpinComponent | write | Read for parameters; accumulated time advanced in place |
| QuadComponent | write | Colour recomputed each frame |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SpinComponent | write | m_Elapsed advanced by the (scaled) frame delta |
| QuadComponent | write | m_Color recomputed from the spin parameters |
| AnimationTransformRequestOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | animated position + rotation for the quad |
